reviewText: I am suprised that this Series has kept me interested one episode after another.  Very good story with a lot of action, suspense, and drama.  Thumbs up for Season 1&2.Despite "Homeland" having men and women in uniform as actors, I recommend all Iraqi and Afghanistan war veterans to watch it.  It gets really deep about the challenges of SGT. Brodies return home after 8 years of captivity, his suffering from PTSD, test of faith and the CIA on his @$$Will be purchasing Season 3 and I cant wait to watch it.
summary: Best TV series I ever watched
